  "title": "Technical Lead - Java",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s Degree in Computer Science, Information      Technology, or related field.</li>\n  <li>8–10 years of experience in enterprise application  development and system integration.</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of experience in a technical  leadership or solution lead role within Corporate/Wholesale Banking domain.</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience designing and deploying applications on OpenShift.</li>\n  <li>Full stack developer, with strong proficiency in Java / J2EE, Spring Framework, RESTful APIs, Microservices architecture, Angular,      ReactJS .</li>\n  <li>Experience with Red Hat OpenShift (containerization,      deployment, scaling, and monitoring).</li>\n  <li>Experience with Jasper &amp; Birt</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in MySQL (schema design, query optimization, stored procedures).</li>\n  <li>CI/CD pipeline tools such as Jenkins, Git, Maven, or   similar.</li>\n  <li>Docker, Kubernetes (added advantage).</li>\n  <li>SOAP/REST APIs, MQ, and event-driven integration  patterns.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with OAuth2, JWT, SSL, and application  security standards.</li>\n  <li>Experience in optimizing backend systems for  scalability and low latency.</li>\n</ul>",
